 Prospective before / after observational clinical multicentric study on ICU acute kidney injury during renal replacement therapy.

 Evaluation of incidence and exposure to hemofilter clotting.

 The after phase will consist in medical measures (help for prescription) and paramedical measures (stop the filtration flow during the patient's mobilization).

